<div id="fb_body_wrapper">
<div id="fb_tab">
<div id="fb_tab_l">Spc</div>
<div id="fb_tab_r">&nbsp;<img src="images/fblogo_mini.gif" /></div> 
</div> 
<div id="fb_pg_wrapper">
<div id="fb_pg_body">
	Fonction qui affiche des espaces suppl&eacute;mentaires lors d'une &eacute;criture &agrave; l'&eacute;cran ou dans un fichier<br \>
<br \>
<div class="fb_sect_title">Syntaxe</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><tt><br \>
<b>Spc</b>( <i>columns</i> )<br \>
</tt><br \>
</div><div class="fb_sect_title">Usage</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><tt><br \>
<a href="KeyPgPrint.html">Print</a> <b>Spc</b>( <i>spaces</i> ) [(, | ;)] ...<br \>
</tt><br \>
</div><div class="fb_sect_title">Param&egrave;tres</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
<tt><i>spaces</i></tt><br \>
<div class="fb_indent">nombre d'espaces &agrave; ajouter<br \>
<br \>
</div></div><div class="fb_sect_title">Description</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
<tt><b>Spc</b></tt> ajoute un certain nombre d'espaces <tt><i>(spaces)</i></tt> lors d'un <tt><a href="KeyPgPrint.html">Print</a></tt> &agrave; l'&eacute;cran ou dans un fichier.  Les cellules caract&egrave;re saut&eacute;es restent inchang&eacute;es.<br \>
<br \>
</div><div class="fb_sect_title">Exemple</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
<tt><div class="freebasic">
<span class="key">Print</span>&nbsp;<span class="quo">"foo"</span><span class="oth">;</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Spc</span><span class="oth">(</span><span class="num">5</span><span class="oth">);</span>&nbsp;<span class="quo">"bar"</span><br />
<span class="key">Print</span>&nbsp;<span class="quo">"hello"</span><span class="oth">;</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Spc</span><span class="oth">(</span><span class="num">4</span><span class="oth">);</span>&nbsp;<span class="quo">"world"</span><br />
</div></tt><br />
<br \>
<tt><div class="freebasic">
<span class="com">''&nbsp;Uses&nbsp;Spc&nbsp;to&nbsp;justify&nbsp;text&nbsp;instead&nbsp;of&nbsp;Tab</span><br />
<br />
<span class="key">Dim</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">As</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">String</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">A1</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">B1</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">A2</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">B2</span><br />
<br />
<span class="wrd">A1</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">=</span>&nbsp;<span class="quo">"Jane"</span><br />
<span class="wrd">B1</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">=</span>&nbsp;<span class="quo">"DOE"</span><br />
<span class="wrd">A2</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">=</span>&nbsp;<span class="quo">"Bob"</span><br />
<span class="wrd">B2</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">=</span>&nbsp;<span class="quo">"Smith"</span><br />
<br />
<span class="key">Print</span>&nbsp;<span class="quo">"FIRST&nbsp;NAME"</span><span class="oth">;</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Spc</span><span class="oth">(</span><span class="num">35</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">-</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">10</span><span class="oth">);</span>&nbsp;<span class="quo">"LAST&nbsp;NAME"</span><br />
<span class="key">Print</span>&nbsp;<span class="quo">"----------"</span><span class="oth">;</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Spc</span><span class="oth">(</span><span class="num">35</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">-</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">10</span><span class="oth">);</span>&nbsp;<span class="quo">"----------"</span><br />
<span class="key">Print</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">A1</span><span class="oth">;</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Spc</span><span class="oth">(</span><span class="num">35</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">-</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Len</span><span class="oth">(</span><span class="wrd">A1</span><span class="oth">));</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">B1</span><br />
<span class="key">Print</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">A2</span><span class="oth">;</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Spc</span><span class="oth">(</span><span class="num">35</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">-</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Len</span><span class="oth">(</span><span class="wrd">A2</span><span class="oth">));</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">B2</span><br />
</div></tt><br />
<br \>
La sortie ressemblera &agrave;:<br \>
<tt><pre class="fb_pre">
FIRST NAME                         LAST NAME
----------                         ----------
Jane                               DOE
Bob                                Smith
</pre></tt><br \>
<br \>
</div><div class="fb_sect_title">Diff&eacute;rences avec QB</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
<ul><li> En QBASIC, des espaces sont imprim&eacute;s dans l'intervalle, tandis que dans FreeBasic, les caract&egrave;res sont simplement saut&eacute;s et laiss&eacute;s intacts.  La fonction <tt><a href="KeyPgSpace.html">Space</a></tt> peut &ecirc;tre utilis&eacute;e dans le m&ecirc;me but.<br \>
<br \>
</ul></div><div class="fb_sect_title">Voir aussi</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
<ul><li> <tt><a href="KeyPgTab.html">Tab</a></tt><br \>
<li> <tt><a href="KeyPgSpace.html">Space</a></tt><br \>
<li> <tt><a href="KeyPgPrint.html">Print</a></tt><br \>
<br \>
</ul></div>
</div>
</div> 
